WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:01.662
Hey, good morning, family.

00:00:01.662 --> 00:00:03.400
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:03.400 --> 00:00:09.346
Well, we're going to do another prayer video, so I hope y'all are ready.

00:00:15.550 --> 00:00:25.369
In the last video, I think it went pretty well for not having done one of those in a while, but thank you for joining me.

00:00:29.100 --> 00:00:37.760
To those that have watched the last one and want to pray again today, thank you again for joining me.

00:00:37.760 --> 00:00:42.049
This would be video number two.

00:00:42.049 --> 00:01:05.800
I'm going to go over the things that the Lord showed me in prayer yesterday, what I was seeing in the spirit, for the people who didn't watch it or are new here.

00:01:05.800 --> 00:01:18.014
I'm going to be praying over the elections and just whatever the Lord puts on my heart.

00:01:18.014 --> 00:01:35.927
As I pray, He just said, 'Brandon, I want you to do 30 days of prayer videos up until the election.

00:01:35.927 --> 00:01:45.895
' Even after, I believe we'll pray even after.

00:01:45.895 --> 00:02:07.860
There are some things that I'm seeing in the spirit that will have to be prayed even after the election is over, from what I've seen.

00:02:17.936 --> 00:02:18.132
It just takes work, but I appreciate you all who want to work with me.

00:02:18.132 --> 00:02:24.994
Okay, so this is what the Lord showed me yesterday.

00:02:24.994 --> 00:02:32.572
I saw a pipeline, like you see at a dam.

00:02:40.027 --> 00:02:47.004
It was a metal pipeline that water was running through; a river, a stream was flowing through this brook, flowing through this pipeline.

00:02:47.004 --> 00:03:03.634
But there were demonic blockages in people's lives that were like tree limbs and rocks, and they were the blackest, like onyx-looking color.

00:03:08.408 --> 00:03:11.708
The darkest of the evil was trying to block the river from flowing freely.

00:03:11.708 --> 00:03:24.972
Whenever I was standing up on the bank in the spirit, looking over this brook, the Lord said, 'Take authority over those blockages.

00:03:24.972 --> 00:03:29.360
' That's what I was praying over.

00:03:29.360 --> 00:03:51.679
When I was praying in the spirit, I could see those tree limbs and the rocks, and they had yellow-looking cat eyes that were bright, neon yellow—a dark yellow, though.

00:03:59.713 --> 00:04:14.856
They had a black center inside of the eye, and they were looking up at me on the bank, kind of like a serpent would look up.

00:04:16.653 --> 00:04:29.090
It was watching, trying to remain disguised as they had a dam trying to block up the flow of the Holy Spirit in some people, trying to hinder them.

00:04:29.090 --> 00:04:45.548
That's what part of the intercessory prayer that we were praying for yesterday was for—spiritual blockages to be released from the people that are praying with us.

00:04:45.548 --> 00:04:52.743
Even me, I'll yield to the Holy Spirit.

00:04:55.115 --> 00:04:57.039
I want a free flow.

00:04:57.039 --> 00:05:03.136
I want more of Him and less of me.

00:05:12.982 --> 00:05:15.293
We have this treasure in earthen vessels, that the excellency of the power will be known of Him and not of us.

00:05:15.293 --> 00:05:25.173
I'm telling you all, we're in a time like we've never seen before.

00:05:25.173 --> 00:05:33.587
Part of what I saw yesterday was the Lord warning me about big gatherings again.

00:05:34.973 --> 00:05:47.040
I was sent an email and even a text from a friend telling me, 'Hey, do you remember praying over Coachella?

00:05:47.040 --> 00:06:11.589
' I've been praying over Coachella, and the Lord will show me things way in advance over events trying to manifest, taking authority over them so they don't happen.

00:06:15.010 --> 00:06:29.243
I saw mass shootings events happening at Coachella, and the Lord said, 'I want you to pray over this event that this does not take place.

00:06:29.243 --> 00:06:38.560
' I thought it was the concert event, and maybe it was; I don't know.

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:41.890
We hear in part and see in part.

00:06:41.890 --> 00:06:54.825
When you're looking through the filter of what the Lord's trying to tell you, you just keep praying.

00:06:55.924 --> 00:07:15.724
I saw that dam and what the Lord was warning me about back in March of last year, and the Lord told me to start praying over this, that this was a serious thing to pray over.

00:07:15.724 --> 00:07:32.835
Well, my friend sent me a text and said, 'Hey, Brandon, did you see that President Donald Trump was going to Coachella to hold a rally there?

00:07:32.835 --> 00:07:37.085
' I had no idea.

00:07:37.085 --> 00:07:53.994
The things that you get in the spirit are warnings, and you try to put your own mind to it and get in trouble because you're thinking it's the concert.

00:07:53.994 --> 00:07:58.520
All I know is that we pray.

00:07:58.520 --> 00:08:12.319
Whether it could be the presidential thing happening this weekend with the speech, I don't know.

00:08:12.319 --> 00:08:20.857
All I know is the Lord warned me to pray over this stuff.

00:08:20.857 --> 00:08:27.240
Did it witness with me that this could be it?

00:08:27.240 --> 00:08:32.939
Yeah, I thought it's more than likely it.

00:08:40.399 --> 00:08:42.988
I don't want to get in the flesh about it, but I'm being real.

00:08:44.550 --> 00:09:07.360
There are certain things I know about October—to pray hedges of protection over President Trump, praying that there is no weapon formed against him that would prosper, or the bystanders, the people in the crowd.

00:09:07.360 --> 00:09:21.383
We pray that all hidden things be revealed and that the enemy would not have any kind of open door for opportunity to rob anybody's life.

00:09:21.383 --> 00:09:26.040
Then the Lord showed me stadiums again.

00:09:26.040 --> 00:09:34.297
When I was praying yesterday, I saw the stadiums again and I kept seeing New York.

00:09:37.693 --> 00:09:43.409
I was praying over New York in these playoff games and the things happening with baseball.

00:09:47.857 --> 00:09:58.608
I don't want to go into a lot of that, but I'm praying over the open stadiums.

00:10:06.896 --> 00:10:12.110
I told you about drones and things like that; remember I warned you all about that?

00:10:12.110 --> 00:10:23.457
I had my son make a short about it, and YouTube flagged it and made me alter some things.

00:10:23.457 --> 00:10:26.836
Whatever, it's their platform.

00:10:26.836 --> 00:10:36.112
I just want to tell you all, we are making a difference.

00:10:36.112 --> 00:10:47.571
I believe we've had over 20,000 people pray with me in that last video.

00:10:47.571 --> 00:10:53.959
I'm excited that you want to pray with me.

00:10:53.959 --> 00:11:05.868
I don't want to keep rambling; I just have some things in my heart before I start praying.

00:11:05.868 --> 00:11:15.337
It's exciting that we are joining together as an army and fighting off the wicked.

00:11:21.244 --> 00:11:29.028
I could feel the push against the darkness when we were praying and the video was going forth throughout the whole world.

00:11:29.028 --> 00:11:53.045
When you have 20,000 people praying—whether it's five minutes or the whole thing—it's like an auditorium or a huge stadium full of people praying in the spirit, asking the Father for His angelic protection and manifestation of glory.

00:11:53.045 --> 00:12:03.080
When we pray together as a family, we're able to do great things together.

00:12:03.080 --> 00:12:24.513
I want to take a moment and just give God thanks for what He's doing in these last days on a YouTube channel, that we have power and authority over the devil.

00:12:24.513 --> 00:12:33.691
We're seated with Him in the heavenlies, far above all principalities, powers, and might.

00:12:33.691 --> 00:12:50.814
I was listening to a revival; we were going to church and there is a healing revival going on right now.

00:12:50.814 --> 00:13:10.088
She was talking about renewing your mind to the Word of God on a day-to-day basis because as soon as you get free, the enemy comes immediately to steal the Word.

00:13:10.088 --> 00:13:17.173
He tries to steal the testimony of your healing or whatever you've been believing for.

00:13:23.519 --> 00:13:28.109
You get your breakthrough and the enemy's already right there trying to take it from you.

00:13:36.679 --> 00:13:39.949
The only way you're able to stand against the devil is by the Word of God.

00:13:47.600 --> 00:13:52.889
It is the Sword of the Spirit and the Shield of Faith that quenches all the fiery darts of the wicked.

00:13:57.987 --> 00:14:02.026
You need to have your sword and your shield up, ready to fight it off.

00:14:02.026 --> 00:14:14.660
The Sword of the Spirit is the Word of Faith, and standing in faith quenches those fiery darts.

00:14:14.660 --> 00:14:27.973
I just want to encourage you that we're not armorless, we're not defeated, and we're not broke, busted, and disgusted.

00:14:31.712 --> 00:14:40.493
The Greater One lives on the inside of you, but you have to get a revelation knowledge of the Word of God inside of you.

00:14:40.493 --> 00:14:48.137
It's not like reading a passage of scripture one time and bypassing it.

00:14:48.137 --> 00:14:56.088
Faith cometh by hearing and hearing by the Word of God.

00:15:00.704 --> 00:15:08.920
If ye abide in Me and My words remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done.

00:15:08.920 --> 00:15:27.099
Dissect that: if you abide in Him and His words, the Bible, remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it will be done.

00:15:27.099 --> 00:15:33.049
That's how your prayers are going to get answered in these last days.

00:15:33.049 --> 00:15:44.200
If your prayers aren't getting answered and you don't see results, check your Word level.

00:15:44.200 --> 00:15:48.020
Check what you're meditating on.

00:15:51.404 --> 00:16:08.769
The more you meditate on the Word and renew your mind, the more that Word gets down inside of you and becomes a rhema word, not just reading scripture.

00:16:08.769 --> 00:16:18.773
I did that, and the Lord asked me, 'Now, what did you learn?

00:16:18.773 --> 00:16:24.177
' I said, 'I don't know if I learned anything.

00:16:24.177 --> 00:16:26.068
' He said, 'Then what good did it do you?

00:16:26.068 --> 00:16:34.107
' You have to understand the Word; you shall know the truth, and the truth will set you free.

00:16:34.107 --> 00:16:41.686
You're wasting your time if you're just reading and getting nothing from it.

00:16:41.686 --> 00:16:49.839
Find just a couple of scriptures and meditate on them all day long until they get down inside of your spirit and become real to you.

00:16:49.839 --> 00:16:59.340
'Greater is He that is in me than he that is in the world.

00:16:59.340 --> 00:17:03.830
' Find those scriptures and write them on flashcards.

00:17:03.830 --> 00:17:08.080
Write it down, make it plain.

00:17:08.080 --> 00:17:16.615
Whenever you have a break at work, pull out that flashcard.

00:17:16.615 --> 00:17:24.880
Put it on your rearview mirror or somewhere you can see it.

00:17:24.880 --> 00:17:34.688
Let those words penetrate inside of you on a day-to-day basis, and the Word of God will change you.

00:17:34.688 --> 00:17:52.1000
It makes you alive and strong, and it feeds your spirit until you become a spiritual giant.

00:17:56.280 --> 00:18:18.600
The devil hates that and is scared of it, but he's not scared of somebody who just reads something without getting revelation in it, thinking, 'Boy, I read my Bible today,' when it isn't doing you any good.

00:18:18.600 --> 00:18:35.552
Unless you're getting it in you, understanding who you are and what He did for you, just keep washing in the water and renewing your mind.

00:18:36.173 --> 00:18:48.280
The Lord challenged me, saying, 'Brandon, I need you to get in the Word even more.

00:18:48.280 --> 00:18:56.835
I need you to memorize even more scripture.

00:18:56.835 --> 00:19:03.340
' He said, 'This is for you too.

00:19:03.340 --> 00:19:06.292
Don't just listen to the preacher; get that Word more inside of you.

00:19:06.292 --> 00:19:16.453
' We're always going from glory to glory.

00:19:16.453 --> 00:19:40.656
We're all a work in progress, whether you got born again yesterday or you've been in this for 50 years.

00:19:40.656 --> 00:19:46.427
None of us have arrived.

00:19:46.427 --> 00:19:58.720
We're always on the potter's wheel until the day we go home.

00:19:58.720 --> 00:20:04.178
Nobody has it all together, and if you think you do, God help you.

00:20:04.178 --> 00:20:14.712
I'm a person who wants to be filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit.

00:20:14.960 --> 00:20:15.704
I hope that helped you.

00:20:21.771 --> 00:20:22.149
You want to know why your prayers aren't getting answered?

00:20:22.149 --> 00:20:27.906
Maybe your Word level's not filled up enough.

00:20:28.258 --> 00:20:33.805
The Word level is like a gas tank.

00:20:33.805 --> 00:20:46.499
When the tank's full, the car runs good; the moment it's running on fumes, you're in trouble.

00:20:46.499 --> 00:21:03.250
You're going to be on the side of the road hitchhiking, saying, 'I need help, AAA, whoever, come and fill my tank up.

00:21:03.250 --> 00:21:14.413
' I want to encourage you today to get in the Word.

00:21:14.413 --> 00:21:21.520
Find scriptures for what you need.

00:21:21.520 --> 00:21:29.159
Maybe you have marriage problems, wayward children, or you're believing for unsaved loved ones.

00:21:29.159 --> 00:21:38.428
Find scriptures that pertain to what you need—healing, deliverance, or whatever—and meditate on them.

00:21:38.428 --> 00:22:04.591
Fill yourself up because the enemy will come immediately to try to take the Word of God from you.

00:22:04.591 --> 00:22:22.750
He doesn't want you to stay healed.

00:22:53.624 --> 00:22:56.880
If you don't fill yourself up with the Word, he comes back with seven more of his buddies and they'll make it even worse.

00:22:56.880 --> 00:23:10.844
The only way you maintain and keep your healing is by keeping yourself full of the Word.

00:23:10.844 --> 00:23:31.260
Take that Sword of the Spirit and cut that devil up and say, 'No, you aren't stealing my healing again.

00:23:38.470 --> 00:23:38.880
This was all paid for by His blood.

00:23:38.880 --> 00:23:48.551
You're not going to come into my house and rob my children or my finances.

00:23:48.551 --> 00:23:58.246
I'm a tither, I'm a giver, I'm a sower, and I'm a believer.

00:23:58.246 --> 00:24:23.770
' Christ has redeemed me from the curse of the law, and if He redeemed me, I'm not underneath that curse of poverty, lack, mental torments, depression, anxiety, or fear.

00:24:27.440 --> 00:24:43.655
Jesus paid the price for you to walk free, and the only way you will be free is if you know the truth.

00:24:43.655 --> 00:24:46.295
His Word is the truth.

00:24:46.295 --> 00:24:57.480
He set the captives free by the blood of the Lamb and the word of their testimony.

00:24:57.480 --> 00:25:06.659
Let's take a moment right now; we're going to pray.

00:25:06.659 --> 00:25:07.964
Father, we thank You.

00:25:11.599 --> 00:25:16.172
We thank You that our electric bills are paid.

00:25:16.172 --> 00:25:22.160
We thank You for our house note—it's paid off in full in Jesus' name.

00:25:22.160 --> 00:25:35.160
Just let it flow out of you; just thank Him today.

00:25:35.160 --> 00:25:42.200
Oh Lord, we thank You.

00:25:42.200 --> 00:25:46.480
You've been so good to us.

00:25:46.480 --> 00:25:52.383
It's real to us, Lord.

00:26:04.054 --> 00:26:04.429
We give You all the glory and honor.

00:26:13.013 --> 00:26:13.608
Thank You for every need that I have, because You met it.

00:26:23.359 --> 00:26:27.960
Thank You for the roof over my head, the car I drive, and the clothes on my back.

00:26:27.960 --> 00:26:47.000
Thank You for the food in my stomach and the air I'm breathing.

00:27:29.497 --> 00:27:29.703
Thank You for everything You've provided, for You have been good to me.

00:27:34.515 --> 00:27:34.900
Thank You, Jesus.

00:27:34.900 --> 00:27:44.147
Thank You that Megan is getting better every day.

00:28:00.016 --> 00:28:00.462
Thank You that she has the mind of Christ.

00:28:09.280 --> 00:28:09.629
Thank You for a good marriage and for my children.

00:28:09.629 --> 00:28:22.640
Thank You that we are all delivered and that we don't have bondage.

00:28:22.640 --> 00:28:26.919
You've been so merciful and wonderful.

00:28:26.919 --> 00:28:31.320
Thank You that we're healed.

00:28:42.679 --> 00:28:45.635
There are so many times we could have died or been in harm's way, and You protected us.

00:28:48.373 --> 00:29:01.956
In the darkest hours and deepest valleys, You were there for me when it seemed all was lost.

00:29:01.956 --> 00:29:11.199
Be grateful for all that you have.

00:29:11.199 --> 00:29:19.753
Thank You, Lord, for what You've already done.

00:29:39.720 --> 00:29:40.040
Thank You that You saved my soul and that my name is written in the Lamb's Book of Life.

00:29:40.040 --> 00:29:46.840
So Father, we come boldly before that throne today.

00:29:59.585 --> 00:30:00.965
We stand in the gap for the people.

00:30:02.960 --> 00:30:13.039
There are a lot of people in harm's way right now with this hurricane.

00:30:32.610 --> 00:30:32.900
Lord, You told me a great storm was coming.

00:30:33.190 --> 00:30:36.668
You said it would be devastating.

00:30:36.668 --> 00:30:50.359
I told everybody this time last year that there's a massive hurricane coming on the East Coast.

00:30:50.359 --> 00:31:02.840
I know some of that's spiritual, but this is serious in the natural.

00:31:07.115 --> 00:31:22.019
You said in Your Word that we have authority over this storm—that we can speak to the storm and call it to dissipate.

00:31:22.019 --> 00:31:35.671
So Father, we speak to this storm in the name of Jesus and we call you to go away.

00:31:35.671 --> 00:31:50.526
We're not going to push you north or south; we take authority over this storm and say, 'We poke its eye out.

00:31:50.526 --> 00:31:56.263
' We call shear to break up that eyewall.

00:32:01.399 --> 00:32:02.199
We say, in the name of Jesus Christ, you dissolve.

00:32:02.199 --> 00:32:11.170
If they're using chemicals to make it strong, we say stop it in the name of Jesus.

00:32:11.170 --> 00:32:16.013
Let all hidden things be revealed.

00:32:16.013 --> 00:32:24.240
For they say this is the strongest hurricane in history, and I say no more.

00:32:34.050 --> 00:32:34.340
Father, I thank You for divine intervention.

00:32:34.340 --> 00:32:43.599
I thank You that even people in the natural would use wisdom.

00:32:43.599 --> 00:32:57.399
I've seen Fort Myers and the Tampa area; I thank You, Lord, that there is no loss of life.

00:33:01.480 --> 00:33:11.568
I call for weakening over this system in Jesus' name.

00:33:13.560 --> 00:33:21.127
I thank You that it will not go inland and destroy all that land.

00:33:21.127 --> 00:33:29.530
We call you to weaken in Jesus' name.

00:33:32.846 --> 00:33:35.519
Father, we just thank You for the presidential elections.

00:33:38.074 --> 00:33:57.780
I thank You that all hidden things be revealed concerning voters—that there will be no fraudulent activities of any kind.

00:33:57.780 --> 00:34:01.300
All hidden things be revealed.

00:34:09.379 --> 00:34:10.640
We pray over the Dominion machines and over all mail-in ballots.

00:34:10.640 --> 00:34:27.240
I thank You, Father, that there is an uncovering of all hidden things in the next couple of weeks.

00:34:39.674 --> 00:34:41.480
I pray a hedge of protection over President Trump right now when he goes to Coachella, that there are no mass casualties.

00:34:41.480 --> 00:34:49.269
There is no storm, no nothing that comes nigh this event.

00:34:57.480 --> 00:35:10.249
The things that You showed me about the mass things that would try to take place there, we say in the name of Jesus, you will not do this.

00:35:10.249 --> 00:35:26.432
There will be no terrorist activities and no calamity in the name of Jesus.

00:35:28.520 --> 00:35:33.160
We cover this event in the blood.

00:35:33.160 --> 00:35:49.040
I thank You that Your angels are going before and protecting, even from the mountains.

00:35:49.040 --> 00:35:54.725
No long-range shooting, no long-range snipers.

00:35:54.725 --> 00:36:07.319
We take authority over snipers and over people; let them be caught.

00:36:31.750 --> 00:36:32.340
We plead the blood over these circumstances and thank You for the hedge of protection.

00:36:33.520 --> 00:36:42.114
Father, we thank You that it'll be a clean, fair election in Jesus' name.

00:36:42.114 --> 00:36:55.680
Every person who's alive and is a legal American citizen will vote.

00:36:55.680 --> 00:37:17.515
I thank You that the blinders would come off their eyes so they would vote godly and righteous, putting in good laws for the land.

00:37:33.606 --> 00:37:33.931
Father, You're not done with America.

00:37:33.931 --> 00:37:38.849
There's one last call, one last harvest.

00:37:38.849 --> 00:37:45.360
As it gets darker, the light will get lighter.

00:37:53.474 --> 00:38:00.383
I call forth a revival in the church with Brush Arbor churches, a Brush Arbor revival, that the church would rise up.

00:38:00.383 --> 00:38:20.195
Father, we call forth a great harvest of lost people out of the darkness and into the light.

00:38:20.195 --> 00:38:26.840
We send forth the laborers right now.

00:38:26.840 --> 00:38:46.580
We call them forth—that people would be bold about their faith and that we would be the salt and light in these last days.

00:38:46.580 --> 00:38:55.914
Let the light of the Lord shine upon our faces like it did Moses.

00:38:55.914 --> 00:39:03.225
Visit us once again, oh God.

00:39:03.225 --> 00:39:26.760
Help us to stand out in a crowd so that when all hell is breaking loose, they would say, 'What's different about you?

00:39:26.760 --> 00:39:58.423
' It's not about how great we are, but about the One who lives on the inside of us.

00:39:58.423 --> 00:40:32.040
As the dark's getting darker, the light's getting lighter on us.

00:40:32.040 --> 00:40:57.346
When calamity hits, there's light in Goshen, and the people would run to the light.

00:41:04.280 --> 00:41:21.915
Father, I thank You that they would go back to church, and when they do, they would get the truth—not some seeker-friendly, watered-down message.

00:41:33.670 --> 00:41:36.446
Father, I thank You that You would burn in the pastors, teachers, and evangelists.

00:41:36.446 --> 00:41:52.520
Raise up a new David in this hour, new warriors who are after Your own heart.

00:41:52.520 --> 00:42:07.720
We pray a fresh fire and fresh anointing on their lives.

00:42:07.720 --> 00:42:23.280
We call fire to stir in them right now, a fresh living water on the inside of them.

00:42:23.280 --> 00:42:31.315
Let them have a new wine, a new presence, a new flame.

00:42:31.315 --> 00:42:40.679
Be filled with the Holy Spirit and with fire.

00:42:40.679 --> 00:42:46.520
We call for a great harvest of souls.

00:42:46.520 --> 00:42:49.920
Visit us one more time, Lord.

00:42:49.920 --> 00:42:54.613
Have mercy on this generation.

00:42:54.613 --> 00:43:00.592
Stir up our pastors, prophets, teachers, and evangelists.

00:43:00.592 --> 00:43:10.696
Bring them back to the altars and to repentance and holiness.

00:43:10.696 --> 00:43:16.573
Shake off the compromise.

00:43:21.120 --> 00:43:29.888
Lord, use us once again for a great outpouring of Your Spirit.

00:43:29.888 --> 00:43:40.022
You're not done with America, Australia, Africa, Asia, Europe, or South America.

00:43:40.022 --> 00:43:43.420
We call for revival.

00:43:43.420 --> 00:44:07.674
We call for the blinders to be removed from people's eyes so they can see freely what Jesus has done.

00:44:29.800 --> 00:44:30.360
I thank You, Lord, that judgment begins in the house of the Lord first.

00:44:33.271 --> 00:44:59.319
I thank You for a fresh touch of the fire of judgment upon the churches to stir up the pastors and those who are lukewarm.

00:44:59.319 --> 00:45:18.480
If they're not right, bring in a new one where there will be an outpouring of Your Spirit like we've never seen before.

00:45:22.076 --> 00:45:23.231
Thank You, Lord, that I'll be one—send me.

00:45:23.231 --> 00:45:44.839
I speak to the people on the internet to warn them that Jesus is coming, to warn them to get their life in order.

00:45:47.973 --> 00:45:48.327
The King is coming!

00:45:48.327 --> 00:45:52.267
I yell it from the mountaintops.

00:45:52.267 --> 00:46:11.200
Like Paul Revere riding in the dark warning that the British are coming, I ride in the midnight warning Your people that You are coming.

00:46:11.200 --> 00:46:18.524
It's time to wake up.

00:46:23.380 --> 00:46:23.695
The ark is closing.

00:46:23.695 --> 00:46:36.826
Wake up, you lost people, for the King is coming.

00:46:40.510 --> 00:46:49.091
The sun is setting on this dispensation of grace.

00:47:13.640 --> 00:47:14.000
Are you awake?

00:47:14.000 --> 00:47:17.257
Have mercy on their souls, Lord.

00:47:17.257 --> 00:47:18.987
Wake them up.

00:47:40.020 --> 00:47:40.335
We pray over the lost.

00:47:40.335 --> 00:47:43.839
Do it again, Lord.

00:47:43.839 --> 00:47:48.759
Anoint us with Your fire.

00:47:59.466 --> 00:48:00.160
We need a fresh touch of the fresh oil in our wineskins.

00:48:07.459 --> 00:48:12.544
Thank You, Holy Spirit, that You abide in us.

00:48:12.544 --> 00:48:22.093
It is the goodness of God that draws men to repentance.

00:48:29.520 --> 00:48:29.849
I pray for a revival in Israel.

00:48:39.190 --> 00:48:39.445
I call peace over Jerusalem.

00:48:42.344 --> 00:48:52.772
I thank You that they would see the error in their ways.

00:48:52.772 --> 00:49:15.393
Visit Israel one last time and show this generation that You are real, just like You were to the children of Israel of old when You delivered them out of Egypt.

00:49:15.393 --> 00:49:26.470
Visit them again and show them that You are 'I Am that I Am.

00:49:26.470 --> 00:49:42.909
' You said it to me before when I was in Your throne, and the foundation shook before my feet.

00:50:00.400 --> 00:50:00.933
You are still 'I Am that I Am.

00:50:00.933 --> 00:50:05.649
' Visit us once again.

00:50:17.645 --> 00:50:20.559
Give us one more touch of Your fresh fire, one more drink of the living water.

00:50:23.919 --> 00:50:24.640
I'll never get enough.

00:50:24.640 --> 00:50:29.989
I'll never stop knocking on Your door.

00:50:29.989 --> 00:50:37.074
I knock and I knock, asking for the anointing.

00:50:37.074 --> 00:50:40.820
Create in us a clean heart, Lord.

00:50:46.620 --> 00:50:46.920
I hear the sound of an abundance of rain.

00:50:53.625 --> 00:50:53.810
Lord, thank You for that sign.

00:50:53.810 --> 00:51:06.493
Now Father, we speak to the drought over the area and we call for rain in the name of Jesus.

00:51:16.720 --> 00:51:16.985
Thank You for rain over Oklahoma, Texas, Missouri, and Kansas.

00:51:28.697 --> 00:51:28.920
The drought is broken in the name of Jesus.

00:51:34.202 --> 00:54:48.810
We call in the Canadian air and the cooler temperatures—not freezing, but cooler.

00:54:48.820 --> 00:58:54.170
We call in the low-pressure systems from the west.

00:58:54.170 --> 00:59:42.630
Bring rain!

00:59:42.630 --> 00:59:50.240
A fresh drink of Your water over our land.

00:59:50.240 --> 01:00:50.955
We call for three inches at least of rain in the name of Jesus, breaking droughts over Lubbock, Pampa, Amarillo, Altus, Oklahoma City, Tulsa, Kansas City, and Wichita.

01:02:27.732 --> 01:02:28.710
Thank You, Father.

01:02:28.720 --> 01:03:38.920
We call our lakes and ponds to fill up so we don't have fires.

01:03:38.920 --> 01:04:02.360
We speak against the natural fires burning up people's land.

01:04:02.360 --> 01:04:16.760
Father, I thank You for a godly President.

01:04:46.450 --> 01:04:46.735
I thank You that Kamala Harris would get born again and that Joe Biden would get radically born again.

01:04:46.735 --> 01:04:53.827
No one is too lost that You can't save them.

01:04:53.827 --> 01:04:57.613
I pray that they would have an experience with You.

01:04:57.613 --> 01:05:12.546
I lift them up and ask for mercy.

01:05:12.546 --> 01:05:23.954
I pray over Donald Trump, Father, for a radical conversion.

01:05:23.954 --> 01:06:04.673
I'm looking for a president who is on fire for Jesus, who prays in tongues in the White House and confesses that Jesus Christ is Lord behind the podium.

01:06:04.673 --> 01:06:19.480
We need someone with a backbone like a crowbar—boldness in faith and in what we stand for.

01:06:19.480 --> 01:06:36.430
We give You glory, honor, and praise for it in Jesus' name.

01:06:36.440 --> 01:07:24.399
Now, for all of you who say, 'What are you going to pray next?

01:07:24.399 --> 01:07:39.120
' I'm going to pray in tongues.

01:07:39.120 --> 01:08:07.672
That's the language of the Spirit, like in Acts chapter 2.

01:08:07.672 --> 01:09:21.630
I'm going to pray in the spirit right now and see if the Lord wants to show me anything.

01:10:47.719 --> 01:10:48.532
Father, I yield my body and spirit to You, that You pray through me in tongues.

01:10:48.532 --> 01:11:17.360
Show me the direction of the Father's heart today.

01:11:17.360 --> 01:11:28.160
There are some of you out there who are believing for the baptism right now.

01:11:30.240 --> 01:12:02.787
Receive the baptism of the Holy Spirit right now in the name of Jesus.

01:12:36.719 --> 01:12:58.427
Now begin to speak with other tongues; He's not going to move your tongue for you, you've got to move your tongue.

01:12:58.427 --> 01:13:19.430
There's a great revival coming for Africa.

01:13:21.120 --> 01:13:26.843
I see it.

01:13:26.843 --> 01:13:31.180
Hallelujah.

01:13:31.180 --> 01:14:00.030
Oh Lord, we thank You for a fresh touch.

01:14:17.552 --> 01:14:18.385
I receive it now in Jesus' name.

01:14:18.385 --> 01:14:30.035
Holy Spirit, You are welcome in this place.

01:14:44.410 --> 01:14:44.740
Lord said to me, 'I want my people to have some joy in this journey.

01:14:44.740 --> 01:14:56.000
' Be happy and full of His joy, for in His presence there is fullness of joy.

01:14:56.000 --> 01:15:02.468
In the days ahead, there shouldn't be dread.

01:15:02.468 --> 01:15:07.587
He wants to fill you with joy.

01:15:07.587 --> 01:15:23.920
Put a song in your heart, singing and making melody unto the Lord with psalms and hymns.

01:15:23.920 --> 01:15:40.639
All the lies told in your ears telling you God doesn't love you are lies.

01:15:47.497 --> 01:15:52.451
I hear fresh revelation of the love of God on you today, for God is love.

01:15:52.451 --> 01:16:00.620
Thank You for Your love for Your church and Your children.

01:16:00.620 --> 01:16:08.080
Come unto Me, and I will give you rest.

01:16:08.080 --> 01:16:15.499
His yoke is easy and His burden is light.

01:16:15.499 --> 01:16:23.396
Thank You, Father, for the healing and restoration of minds.

01:16:23.396 --> 01:16:27.600
We worship You today.

01:16:34.440 --> 01:16:36.990
The glory of the Lord is here.

01:16:36.990 --> 01:16:41.120
Jesus—there's just something about Your name.

01:16:41.120 --> 01:16:53.525
Savior, Jesus, like a fragrance after the rain.

01:16:53.525 --> 01:17:08.908
Let all heaven and earth proclaim: kings and kingdoms will all pass away, but there's something about Your name.

01:17:08.908 --> 01:17:14.244
In this atmosphere, you can get anything—healing or deliverance.

01:17:14.244 --> 01:17:22.747
Reach up and just grab a hold of it by faith.

01:17:22.747 --> 01:17:26.120
Say, 'I receive it now.

01:17:26.120 --> 01:17:35.940
' I can sense His mighty presence in the very atmosphere.

01:17:35.940 --> 01:17:43.903
Reach out and say, 'It's mine, I take it now.

01:17:43.903 --> 01:17:45.159
' You just have to receive it.

01:17:49.647 --> 01:17:50.080
I get lost in His presence.

01:17:52.447 --> 01:17:56.871
This is why people ask how long I pray.

01:17:56.871 --> 01:18:03.787
It's just a lifestyle; you don't time God.

01:18:09.191 --> 01:18:09.453
You don't talk to the King that way.

01:18:10.239 --> 01:18:14.420
You flow until He says you're released.

01:18:14.420 --> 01:18:23.159
Most people have no idea what a relationship is like.

01:18:31.040 --> 01:18:37.840
You don't tell your spouse you're only going to talk for 15 minutes and then be done.

01:18:42.845 --> 01:18:43.230
A relationship is not a time clock.

01:18:43.230 --> 01:18:44.975
It's real.

01:18:44.975 --> 01:18:48.702
That's where you see demonstrations and manifestations.

01:18:48.702 --> 01:18:54.475
He inhabits the praises of His people.

01:18:54.475 --> 01:18:58.000
It's a river; you don't control a river.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
The river is always flowing.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
The Holy Spirit is always flowing; He's not stagnant.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
I think that's good for today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
I appreciate every one of you who joined me.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
I feel like we got some stuff accomplished today.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Tomorrow we'll do it again.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.050
I will set time aside to pray with you all for the election, the storms, and that Jesus becomes real to the people.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
If you're new here, please like my video and subscribe.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
It helps with the algorithm.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Comment something nice down below.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
Click the notification bell.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
God bless every single one of you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Jesus loves you so much.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Have a wonderful day full of joy.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
May the Lord bless you and keep you, may His face shine upon you, and give you peace.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Goodbye.
